\c 24 Mufananidzo wetswanda mbiri dzina maonde 24 1 Zvino Nebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi wakati atapa Jekonia mwanakomana waJehoiakimu, mambo waJudha, namachinda aJudha, pamwechete navavezi navapfuri, paJerusaremu, akavaisa Bhabhironi, Jehovha akandiratidza, ndikaona tswanda mbiri dzina maonde dzakanga dzakaiswa pamberi petemberi yaJehovha. 2 Imwe tswanda yakanga ina maonde akanaka kwazvo, samaonde anotanga kuibva; asi imwe tswanda yakanga inarnaonde akaipa kwazvo, asingabviri kudyiwa nokuipa kwawo. 3 Ipapo Jehovha akati kwandiri, "Unowoneiko Jeremiya?" Ini ndikati, "Maonde; maonde akanaka, akanaka kwazvo, asi akaipa kwazvo, asingabviri kudyiwa nokuipa kwawo." 4 Ipapo shoko raJehovha rakauya kwandiri, richiti, 5 "Zvanzi naJehovha, Mwari waIsiraeri, `Sezvakaita maonde awa akanaka, ndizvo zvandicharangarira nomwoyo wakanaka vatapwa vaJudha, vandakatuma vabve panyika ino vaende kunyika yavaKaradhea. 6 Nokuti ndichavatarira nameso angu nomwoyo wakanaka, ndivadzoserezve kunyika ino; ndichavavaka, handingavakoromori; ndichavasima, handingavadzuri. 7Ndichavapa mwoyo wokundiziva, kuti ndini Jehovha; ivo vachava vanhu vangu, neni ndichava Mwari wavo; nokuti vachadzokera kwandiri nomwoyo wavo wose.' 8 "Uye, sezvakaita maonde akaipa, asingabviri kudyiwa nokuipa kwawo, zvirokwazvo ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha ndizvo zvandichaita Zedhekia mambo waJudha, namachinda ake, navakasara veJerusaremu, vakasara panyika ino, navagere panyika yeljipiti. 9Ndichavaita
